description: Erika & Chad, a husband and wife team, shared a dream to serve the people of Denver the highest-quality handcrafted ice cream. Now High Point Creamery has hit the streets and as they witness the locals loving every lick of their artisan creations...they consider their fantasy to be successfully fulfilled. A few of the flavors you’ll find in their heavenly selection include S’mores, Basil with Blackberry Swirl, Brown Butter Pecan, Earl Grey with Shortbread Cookies, Chocolate Coconut, just to name a few. For some scoops, shakes, floats, and more, head straight over to High Point Creamery and elevate your day the delicious way.
name: High Point Creamery
